	(gr_text_box "Left To Do\nFinish Antenna design, move matching network\nAdd RGB to existing system under the keycaps. maybe even a provision for underglow\n\nHall and AS5600s on breakout PCV's  \n6 wire soldered 1.26mm pitch cable for onew, 4 wire for the other (can link to another connector externally)\nFinalize LIPO location\nMaybe bump the USB annd antenna out just a little"
